        {
            "+content": "Anna Akechi is a second-year middle school student who lives in Makotomirai Town. She travels back in time from 2027 to 1999 when her fairy partner named Pochitan appears on her birthday. In Makotomirai City in 1999, Anna meets Mikuru Kobayashi, another second-year middle school student who dreams of becoming a star detective. The two girls witness the troubles caused by the Phantom Thieves who steal people's precious belongings. They transform into Star Detective Precures and use their deductive reasoning skills to protect people's smiles.",
            "+@gid": "2072472764",
            "+@type": "Plot Summary"
        },
